  "texts": [
    "Based on the findings, a substantial proportion of organizations have either already incorporated or are planning to integrate AI and ML into their cybersecurity initiatives.",
    "These results underscore the growing recognition of the transformative potential of AI and ML in fortifying defensive measures against cyber threats.",
    "Specifically, the survey discovered that 45% of organizations have already integrated AI and ML into their cybersecurity systems, and an additional 35% are planning to do so in the near future.",
    "Applications of AI and ML in cybersecurityThe most commonly reported applications of AI and ML in cybersecurity were intrusion detection and response (62%), malware detection (45%), and network security (40%).",
    "Other notable applications included threat intelligence (35%), incident response (30%), and vulnerability management (25%)."
